    <item>
      <title>Arduino Functions</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/functions/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Dec 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/functions/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;digital-io&#34;&gt;Digital IO&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;digitalRead()-&lt;/strong&gt; it reads a value from an specific pin as either HIGH OR LOW&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;example-code&#34;&gt;Example code&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&#xA;void setup() {&#xA;&#xA;  pinMode(7, INPUT);    // sets the digital pin 7 as input&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;void loop() {&#xA;  val = digitalRead(7);   // read the input pin&#xA;&#xA;}&#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;digitalWrite() -&lt;/strong&gt; -It writes &lt;code&gt;HIGH&lt;/code&gt; OR &lt;code&gt;LOW&lt;/code&gt; value to a digital pin&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;example&#34;&gt;Example&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;void setup() {&#xA;  pinMode(12, OUTPUT);    // sets the digital pin 12 as output&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;void loop() {&#xA;  digitalWrite(12, HIGH); // sets the digital pin 12 on&#xA;  delay(1000);            // waits for a second&#xA;  digitalWrite(12, LOW);  // sets the digital pin 12 off&#xA;  delay(1000);            // waits for a second&#xA;}&#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;pinMode() -&lt;/strong&gt; -it sets specified pin to behave as input or output&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
